{"id":172675,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/08/global-voices-南韩：41人死于山洪土石流/","date":"2011-08-17T07:30:24Z","modified":"2011-08-17T07:30:24Z","title":"Global Voices | 南韩：41人死于山洪土石流","content":"<p><p>[本文英文版原载于2011年7月28日]</p>\n<p>连续不停好几天的豪雨猛烈的冲击着南韩，导致土石流、水灾和停电。至少造成41人死亡，而且仍有12人失踪。在经历灾难的这段期间，南韩持续分享最新消息，透过Twitter上传照片以及给受影响者的建议。</p>\n<p><strong>许多的灾难</strong></p>\n<p>在许多灾难中，<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.travelblog.org/Topics/9513-1.html\" href=\"http://www.travelblog.org/Topics/9513-1.html\">牛眠山</a>因为豪雨导致了土石流，此消息震惊了南韩人。这起事件夺去了32人的生命，其中有十名是做志工的大学生。这座山位于首都首尔的中心，仍有当年韩战所埋放的地雷，这样的威胁引起大众恐惧。</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.wikitree.co.kr/main/news_view.php?id=40828\"><img title=\"Heavy downpours cause flooding in Gyeong-gi Province, South Korea.\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/floodingingyunggi-375x281.jpg\" alt=\"Heavy downpours cause flooding in Gyeong-gi Province, South Korea, Image by Twitter user @karistuck, Posted on the Wiki Tree site (CC BY 2.0).\" width=\"375\" height=\"281\" /></a></p>\n<p>连日不断的豪雨导致南韩京畿道水灾。图片由Twitter使用者@karistuck所提供，张贴于網絡新闻网Wiki Tree，依据创用CC授权使用。</p>\n</div>\n<p>南韩知名者Twitter使用者之一<em>Dogsul</em>（<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/dogsul\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/dogsul\">@dogsul</a>），粉丝超过110,000人，于7月27日张贴了<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/dogsul/status/96227670534258689\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/dogsul/status/96227670534258689\">讯息</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>牛眠山山崩让我担心的事之一，就是伤人地雷。在战争期间，牛眠山是使用地雷最密集的地方。这里有一则相关的<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.sisainlive.com/news/articleView.html?idxno=8130\" href=\"http://www.sisainlive.com/news/articleView.html?idxno=8130\">文章</a>。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>在7月28日的早晨，一则<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://news.nate.com/view/20110728n08311?mid=n0407\" href=\"http://news.nate.com/view/20110728n08311?mid=n0407\">当地新闻</a>引用一名军方高层，确认有十颗地雷因洪水而不知去向。</p>\n<p>Twitter使用者<em><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/funpt\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/funpt\">Funpt</a></em>则上传了<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/funpt/status/96079961785507840\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/funpt/status/96079961785507840\">三张照片</a>，皆为住在山边附近的居民所拍摄：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>一片混乱的牛眠山。<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitpic.com/5wf1a0\" href=\"http://t.co/ETHPknS\">twitpic.com/5wf1a0</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitpic.com/5wf1a1\" href=\"http://t.co/abSsXs1\">twitpic.com/5wf1a1</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitpic.com/5wf1a2\" href=\"http://t.co/q9yAlei\">twitpic.com/5wf1a2 </a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitpic.com/5wf1a1\"><img title=\"Woo-myun mountain in chaos.\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/mountain-chaos-375x281.jpg\" alt=\"Woo-myun mountain in chaos. Image by @Funpt.\" width=\"375\" height=\"281\" /></a></p>\n<p>陷入一片混乱的牛眠山。照片由@Funpt所提供。</p>\n</div>\n<p>Oh Ja-young（<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/urpurple\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/urpurple\">@urpurple</a>）则是在Twitter上<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/urpurple/status/96143129903763456\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/urpurple/status/96143129903763456\">连结</a>到一个关于山崩的公民媒体视频：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>这是牛眠山山崩的景象：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://tvpot.daum.net/clip/ClipView.do/?clipid=34564541&#038;rtes=y\" href=\"http://t.co/qKMu5rL\">tvpot.daum.net/clip/ClipViewB…</a> […]电影海云台（Haeundae）根本无法跟这事件相比，我们就像是在看恐怖片一样。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Landslide Photo by Twitterer\" href=\"http://www.wikitree.co.kr/main/news_view.php?id=40837\"><img title=\"Photos of apartments near the Woo-myun mountain. Image by Twitter user @stella868, Posted on the Wiki Tree site (CC BY 2.0).\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/apt_near_woomyeonmt-224x300.jpg\" alt=\"Photos of apartments near the Woo-myun mountain. Image by Twitter user @stella868, Posted on the Wiki Tree site (CC BY 2.0).\" width=\"234\" height=\"314\" /></a></p>\n<p>牛眠山附近的公寓。照片由Twitter使用者@stella868提供，张贴于Wiki Tree，依据创用CC授权使用。</p>\n</div>\n<p><strong>追究责任</strong></p>\n<p>徐亨旭（<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/minariboy\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/minariboy\">@minariboy</a>）是一个足球评论员，他<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/minariboy/status/96209496396939264\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/minariboy/status/96209496396939264\">指摘</a>首尔市长<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oh_Se-hoon\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oh_Se-hoon\">吴世勋</a>和让他当选市长的江南区人民。江南是富裕的区域之一，也是这次灾情最严重的地区：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>这个人能成为首尔市长是因为在江南区获得压倒性大胜利。在过去五年间，他逐渐减少防洪预算，直至只有当初预算的十分之一。结果，牛眠山于今天崩塌了，电力中断，江南区的大峙站和江南站被洪水淹没。江南人民的选票，给他们带来这场灾难。投票真的是很重要的一件事。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><em><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/peristory\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/peristory\">Pristory</a></em>是一个非营利组织的Twitter帐号，为一般民众分析经济政策，并保护消费者权益。在Twitter<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/peristory/status/96155464504573953\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/peristory/status/96155464504573953\">说</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>山崩发生在瑞草区方背洞的牛眠山，已经让一辆车滑下，并卡在一栋大楼的三楼。<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitpic.com/5wkokg\" href=\"http://twitpic.com/5wkokg\">http://twitpic.com/5wkokg</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://news.mt.co.kr/mtview.php?no=2011072809463741966&#038;type=1\" href=\"http://news.mt.co.kr/mtview.php?no=2011072809463741966&#038;type=1\">有人认为</a>会发生山崩有一部分是因为牛眠山附近的隧道建造，但<em><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/peristory\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/peristory\">Peristory</a></em><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/peristory/status/96190358966370304\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/peristory/status/96190358966370304\">指出</a>另一个原因：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>这次山崩是“自私”造成的吗？瑞草区一开始是为了防止山崩而计划。但是因为百分之97的土地为私人所拥有，反对的声浪强烈到让他们无法开始建设。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.wikitree.co.kr/main/news_view.php?id=40837\"><img title=\"Cars struggling in Gangnam area, Seoul, South Korea\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/flood2.jpg\" alt=\"Cars struggling in Gangnam area, Seoul, South Korea, Image by Twitter user @westminia, Posted on the Wiki Tree site (CC BY 2.0)\" width=\"263\" height=\"194\" /></a></p>\n<p>首尔市江南区的汽车艰难地行进。照片由Twitter使用者@westminia提供，张贴于Wiki Tree，依据创用CC授权使用。</p>\n</div>\n<p><strong>夹缝中求处理</strong></p>\n<p>首尔的商业区因大雨发生水灾，这里每天都有成千上万的人通勤工作，车在湿透的道路上艰难地行进。</p>\n<p>Twitter使用者<em><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/knowledge_bot\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/knowledge_bot\">knowledge_but</a></em><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/knowledge_bot/status/96195040854024192\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/knowledge_bot/status/96195040854024192\">说</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>当你因穿越洪水区或绕道而挣扎时，先估计水的高度并与车轮的高度比较，若水位低于轮胎高度的三分之一，或货车轮胎的二分之一，你就可以开车驶过洪水区。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/knowledge_bot/status/96195098148220929\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/knowledge_bot/status/96195098148220929\">他之后又说</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>开车过水坑时，请将车速降低，用一档或二档。当你经过这个水坑时，可以轻轻煞车器几次，把湿透的煞车片弄干。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.wikitree.co.kr/main/news_view.php?id=40837\"><img title=\"Flood in Hongdae area, Seoul, South Korea.\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/flood1.jpg\" alt=\"Flood in Hongdae area, Seoul, South Korea. Image by net user 케이머스, Posted on the Wiki Tree site (CC BY 2.0)\" width=\"158\" height=\"210\" /></a></p>\n<p>首尔宏大区的洪水泛滥。图片由網絡使用者케이머스所提供，张贴于Wiki Tree，依据创用CC授权使用。</p>\n</div>\n<p>今天大雨也持续着，更多照片与报导像洪水般涌进Twitter圈中。预计未来的24小时里将有更多雨水，网民们已经创建<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://maps.google.com/maps/ms?msa=0&#038;msid=203912538476863310029.0004a9030673b505782a9#bmb=1\" href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps/ms?msa=0&#038;msid=203912538476863310029.0004a9030673b505782a9#bmb=1\">Google地图</a>标记受损地区。</p>\n<p>更新：7月29日死亡人数已达59人。关于首尔市长删减防洪预算导致这次灾难的指控，警方已断定为谣言并且展开调查，搜索網絡中第一个散播不实资讯的人，当地新闻<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://media.daum.net/society/affair/view.html?cateid=1010&#038;newsid=20110729104214883&#038;p=newsis&#038;RIGHT_COMM=R5\" href=\"http://media.daum.net/society/affair/view.html?cateid=1010&#038;newsid=20110729104214883&#038;p=newsis&#038;RIGHT_COMM=R5\">报导</a>。</p>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Soup\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80%85:Soup\">Soup</a></div>\n<p><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/yooeun/\" title=\"文章导读 Lee Yoo Eun\">Lee Yoo Eun</a> · 译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/gvzhteam/\" title=\"文章导读 GV 中文化小组\">GV 中文化小组</a> </span> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/07/28/south-korea-41-dead-in-torrential-flooding-and-landslides/\" title=\"阅读原文 [en]\">阅读原文 [en]</a> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2011/08/17/9669/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%A9%EF%BC%9A41%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%8E%E5%B1%B1%E6%B4%AA%E5%9C%9F%E7%9F%B3%E6%B5%81&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F08%2F17%2F9669%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F08%2F17%2F9669%2F&#038;desc=%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%A9%EF%BC%9A41%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%8E%E5%B1%B1%E6%B4%AA%E5%9C%9F%E7%9F%B3%E6%B5%81\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=%22javascript:var%20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F08%2F17%2F9669%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F08%2F17%2F9669%2F&#038;text=%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%A9%EF%BC%9A41%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%8E%E5%B1%B1%E6%B4%AA%E5%9C%9F%E7%9F%B3%E6%B5%81&#038;via=globalvoiceszh\" title=\"twitter\"><span>twitter</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://reddit.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F08%2F17%2F9669%2F&#038;title=%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%A9%EF%BC%9A41%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%8E%E5%B1%B1%E6%B4%AA%E5%9C%9F%E7%9F%B3%E6%B5%81\" title=\"reddit\"><span>reddit</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.stumbleupon.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F08%2F17%2F9669%2F&#038;title=%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%A9%EF%BC%9A41%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%8E%E5%B1%B1%E6%B4%AA%E5%9C%9F%E7%9F%B3%E6%B5%81\" title=\"StumbleUpon\"><span>StumbleUpon</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://del.icio.us/post?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F08%2F17%2F9669%2F&#038;title=%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%A9%EF%BC%9A41%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%8E%E5%B1%B1%E6%B4%AA%E5%9C%9F%E7%9F%B3%E6%B5%81\" title=\"delicious\"><span>delicious</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.instapaper.com/edit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F08%2F17%2F9669%2F&#038;title=%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%A9%EF%BC%9A41%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%8E%E5%B1%B1%E6%B4%AA%E5%9C%9F%E7%9F%B3%E6%B5%81\" title=\"Instapaper\"><span>Instapaper</span></a></span>\n</p>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":505,"categories":[1],"tags":[]}